** UP1/UP2
0DELETE
1CHANGE
2ADDITION
** MSG
E-01 INPUT RENEW CODE.
E-02 INPUT ORDER NUMBER.
E-03 INPUT ITEM NUMBER.
E-04 THIS DATA IS NOT IN DAYLY ORDER DATA FILE.
E-05 THIS DATA ALREADY HAS BEEN CANCEL.
E-06 THIS DATA ALREADY HAS BEEN INPUT.
E-07 INPUT Q'TY PAR BOX.
E-08 INPUT BOX Q'TY.
E-09 INPUT DIE NUMBER.
E-10 THIS DATA IS NOT IN DIE KANBAN MASTER.
E-11 THE DATA IS ALREADY COMPLETED.
E-12 THIS ITEM NO. HAS BEEN ALREADY USED.
E-13 INPUT DATA IS NOT CORRECT.
E-14 THIS ORDER NO. HAS BEEN ALREADY USED.
E-15 ORDER NO. MORE THAN 50 IS AVAILABLE FOR ORDER ADDITION.
E-16 ITEM NO. MORE THAN 90001 IS AVAILABE FOR ITEM ADDITION.
E-17 NOT INPUT ORDER NO. OF ADDITIONAL ORDER.
E-18 NOT INPUT ITEM NO. OF ADDITIONAL ORDER.
